title: high school musical: the musical: the series
subtitle: season 01
description: will be the first to admit that i thought this was genuinely going to be terrible and an abomination by disney standards, and was delightfully surprised to see how much heart this series has. it's teenagers being teenagers, who also happen to be brilliantly talented, and just plain funny at times.

title: spinning out
subtitle: season 01
description: the intrigue of competitive skating meets canadian ice dancing royalty drama we've always wanted, delivered in a netflix production with quick plot progressions and character arcs on fast-forward.
